Disease: high blood pressure
Nutrients to avoid: high sodium and high fat
Foods to avoid: pickles, canned chicken noodle soup, sauerkraut, french fries, bacon, whole milk, pot pie, donuts, ramen noodles, margarine, sugar alcohol, red meat, table salt

Disease: diabetes
